      <title>本周全球大宗商品市场值得关注的五大关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[甚至在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周六宣布征收大范围进口关税之前，人们对他将采取何种措施的猜测就已推动金价创下自 3 月以来的最大月度涨幅。与此同时，页岩油气开采活动显示出放缓的迹象。尽管全球对能源转型的投资超过 2 万亿美元，但针对气候相关公司的融资交易却在减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大能源公司通过降低关税避免灾难，Gulf Outlet</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/canadian-energy-dodges-cataclysm-with-lower-tariffs-gulf-outlet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令降低原油关税，并可能让生产商完全避免对部分原油征收关税，加拿大的能源行业可能暂时躲过了与美国贸易战的灾难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/canadian-energy-dodges-cataclysm-with-lower-tariffs-gulf-outlet</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 21:55:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家称关税战可能使加拿大陷入衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/tariff-war-likely-to-plunge-canada-into-recession</link>
      <description><![CDATA[顶级经济学家表示，如果关税战持续下去，加拿大经济将面临自新冠疫情以来最严重的冲击，并可能陷入衰退，其中一位经济学家称其为“生存威胁”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/tariff-war-likely-to-plunge-canada-into-recession</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 21:12:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
